carbon-icons-svelte v10.9.2-rc.0
Svelte components for icons in digital and software products using the Carbon Design System.
Install
yarn add carbon-icons-svelte
Usage
Select an icon on the right to view its import path.
Icon name
Icon module name (XX is size)
